ains in Somalia]] *[[List of mountains in South Africa]] *[[List of mountains in South Sudan]] *[[List of mountains in Sudan]] *[[List of mountains in Swaziland]] *[[List of mountains in Tanzania]] *[[List of mountains in Togo]] *[[List of mountains in Tristan da Cunha]] *[[List of mountains in Tunisia]] *[[List of mountains in Uganda]] *[[List of mountains in Western Sahara]] *[[List of mountains in Zambia]] *[[List of mountains in Zimbabwe]] {{div col end}}
