{{DISPLAYTITLE:''Lizzie McGuire'' books}} {{Unreferenced|date=December 2009}} The [[television show]] ''[[Lizzie McGuire]]'' has several books associated. These include '''Jr. Novels''' (which contain stories based on the TV series, with two in each book), '''Mysteries''' (has [[Nancy Drew]]-style mystery books), and other special books which may be about Lizzie's life, survival guides or episode guides. There are also "Cine-manga" pictorial adaptations, using still pictures from the TV series in comic-book manner, published by [[TOKYOPOP]].
