[[Samoa]] requires its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display '''[[vehicle registration plate]]s'''.<ref>http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/PA_SAMO.html</ref> Current plates are [[Vehicle registration plates of Australia|Australian standard]] 372 mm × 134 mm, and use Australian and [[Vehicle registration plates of New Zealand|New Zealand]] stamping dies, as zeroes now have a slash through them (e.g. 52Ø9, 128Ø7).<ref>http://www.plateshack.com/y2k/Samoa/samoay2k.html</ref> {|class="wikitable" |- !Image !First issued !Design !Slogan !Serial format !Serials issued !Notes |- |[[File:Samoa license plate graphic.png|150px]] |1979 | | | | | |- |[[File:WESTERN SAMOA 1979-2000 government license plate Flickr - woody1778a.jpg|150px]] |1979 | | | | |government |- |[[File:Samoa license plate 5511 2000-2010.jpg|150px]] |2000 | | | | | |- |}
